<h3>Usage</h3>
<div class="component-usage">
  <p>Buttons are used to trigger actions or events, such as submitting a form, opening a dialog, canceling an action, or performing a delete operation.</p>

  <h4>When to use</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>Use buttons to trigger an action or event.</li>
    <li>Use links to navigate to a different page or location within the page.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Implementation</h4>

  <pre><code class="language-html">&lt;button class="btn"&gt;Button Text&lt;/button&gt;</code></pre>

  <h4>Available modifiers</h4>
  <ul>
    <li><code>btn-secondary</code>: Secondary button style</li>
    <li><code>btn-outline</code>: Outline button style</li>
    <li><code>btn-danger</code>: Danger/delete button style</li>
    <li><code>btn-success</code>: Success/confirm button style</li>
    <li><code>btn-sm</code>: Small button</li>
    <li><code>btn-lg</code>: Large button</li>
    <li><code>btn-block</code>: Full-width button</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Parameters</h4>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Parameter</th>
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>text</code></td>
        <td>String</td>
        <td>The button text (required)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>modifier</code></td>
        <td>String</td>
        <td>CSS class modifiers (optional)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>disabled</code></td>
        <td>Boolean</td>
        <td>Whether the button is disabled (optional)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>type</code></td>
        <td>String</td>
        <td>Button type attribute (default: "button")</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>iconLeft</code></td>
        <td>HTML</td>
        <td>Icon to display before text (optional)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>iconRight</code></td>
        <td>HTML</td>
        <td>Icon to display after text (optional)</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

